## Key Fixes (Current)

- **Near-uniform basins**: Root cause was `to_simplex(np.ones(64))` in adapter.py bootstrap
  and fallback. Fixed with `hash_to_basin()` for text-dependent non-uniform basins.
- **0 kernels synthesised**: KernelVoice.generate() empty text now falls through to
  LLM-only path instead of returning None.
- **Training trigger**: POST /training/trigger sends QLoRA job to Modal GPU.
  UI button in Training.tsx dashboard.

## Code Style

- Python: ruff check + ruff format, mypy strict mode
