- `modal deploy modal/vex_qlora_train.py` — GPU training (QLoRA)
- `modal deploy modal/vex_coordizer_harvest.py` — GPU harvest
- Image MUST include `fastapi[standard]` for web endpoints
- Image MUST pin `qig-core[torch]>=2.1.0`
- harvest_model MUST match inference_model for token ID alignment in resonance bank

